CBRE are pleased to offer 2 commercial suites at 136 - 140 Victoria Road, Gladesville to the market for sale via an auction campaign.

Located on the ground floor of the premium 83-unit 'Wharf Square' development, anchored by Beacon Lighting. Become part of this revitalised precinct and take advantage of the prominent Victoria Road position with over 300 newly developed apartments in the precinct, more coming in the next 12 months.

Main features include;

SUITE 1
Vacant 125sqm* over 2 floors NLA with Parking
Will suit professional services, creative industries or retail
Excellent main road exposure with 50,763 cars passing daily (RMS)

SUITE 2 & 3
Vacant 202sqm* indoor + 63sqm* outdoor NLA + Parking
Potential to divide space
Will suit food and beverage outlet or a multitude of other uses
Plaza frontage

The property will be sold by auction on Tuesday 15th August 2017 at 10.30am. Auctionworks, 50 Margaret Street, Sydney.
